Dubai
In this role your responsibilities will include, but not be limited to, maintaining and respecting set risk limits and parameters, pricing, trading and risk monitoring systems, and meeting budget targets (P&L;).
The successful candidate should have the following skills:
Previous experience of risk management systems (ideally Front Arena) Experience in ensuring that set risk limits and risk parameters are respected Experience implementing products correctly with the risk monitoring system 2+ years experience in or knowledge of financial sector University degree in finance/ economics/ or mathematics/ physics with a finance degree Languages – Fluency in English and German preferred
If you have the relevant skills and experience and feel you are right for the job, please contact: irina.oprea@swisslinx.com
